        </div>

        <div class="info-container">
            <div class="information">
                <div class="orgName gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>組織名稱</label></div>
                    <div class="description"><p>深夜九點半搶銀行</p></div>
                    <div class="websiteURL"><a href="#">https://robbank.shownest.cc</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="website gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>網站</label></div>
                    <div class="websiteURL"><a href="#">https://other_robbank_website.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="desc gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>描述</label></div>
                    <div class="description"><p>專業團隊提供刺激搶劫服務，保證安全與隱私。最新搶劫任務、專業技巧一應俱全。加入我們，體驗刺激搶銀行之旅！滿足您的刺激需求！滿足您的刺激需求！</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="facebook gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>Facebook 粉絲團網址</label></div>
                    <div class="websiteURL"><a href="#">https://robbank.facebook.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="twitter gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>Twitter 帳號</label></div>
                    <div class="websiteURL"><a href="#">https://robbank.twitter.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flickr  gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>Flickr 相簿網址</label></div>
                    <div class="websiteURL"><a href="#">https://robbank.flickr.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feeback-mail gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>回覆 E-mail 地址</label></div>
                    <div class="websiteURL"><a href="#">robbank@gmail.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="contect-opt gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>顯示/隱藏 「聯絡主辦單位」</label></div>
                    <div class="description"><p>顯示</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="privacy gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>隱私權政策</label></div>
                    <div class="websiteURL"><a href="#">https://robbank.com.privacy</a></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="advancedSetting">
                <div class="img-container gap">
                <div class="info-title"><label>圖像</label></div>
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/250/250/?random=10">
                </div>
                <div class="contact-settings gap">
                    <h3 class="contact-info">聯絡資訊</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="contactName gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>聯絡人名稱</label></div>
                    <div class="description"><p>頭哥</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="mobile gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>聯絡人行動電話</label></div>
                    <div class="description"><p>0912345678</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="tel gap">
                    <div class="info-title"><label>聯絡人一般電話</label></div>
                    <div class="description"><p>02-24567890</p></div>
                </div>
            <div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</section>
